    "Always charges at a minimum rate to ensure some progress. Any extra solar power on top is used to charge faster.": {
      "comment": "Description of a charging mode where the car charges at a minimum rate to ensure some progress, with any extra solar power used to charge faster.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lader altid med en minimumseffekt for at sikre fremskridt. Overskydende solenergi bruges til at lade hurtigere."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lädt immer mit einer Mindestleistung, damit das Laden vorankommt. Zusätzlich verfügbarer Solarstrom wird ebenfalls zum Laden genutzt."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Charge toujours à une puissance minimale pour garantir une progression. Tout surplus solaire est utilisé pour accélérer la charge."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Carica sempre a una potenza minima per garantire un progresso. L'eventuale energia solare in eccesso viene utilizzata per caricare più velocemente."
          }
        }
      }
    },
