    "Charges a specific amount of energy (kWh) by a deadline you set. Solar power is preferred when available.": {
      "comment": "Description of a charging mode where the user specifies a target energy consumption in kilowatt-hours (kWh) and a deadline for reaching that target. Solar power is preferred when available.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Oplader en bestemt mængde energi (kWh) inden en deadline, du vælger. Solenergi foretrækkes, når den er tilgængelig."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lädt eine bestimmte Energiemenge (kWh) bis zu einem von dir festgelegten Zeitpunkt. Solarstrom wird bevorzugt verwendet."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Charge une quantité d'énergie spécifique (kWh) avant une échéance que vous définissez. L'énergie solaire est privilégiée."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Carica una quantità specifica di energia (kWh) entro una scadenza impostata. L'energia solare viene preferita quando disponibile."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Charges at a fixed power level that you choose, regardless of solar production.": {
      "comment": "Description of a charging mode where the car charges at a fixed power level that the user chooses, regardless of solar production.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lader med et fast effektniveau, som du vælger, uanset solproduktion."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lädt mit einer festen Leistung deiner Wahl, unabhängig von der Solarproduktion."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Charge à une puissance fixe que vous choisissez, indépendamment de la production solaire."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Carica a una potenza fissa scelta da te, indipendentemente dalla produzione solare."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Charges at maximum power immediately, regardless of solar production or electricity tariff.": {
      "comment": "Description of a charging mode called \"Always Charge\".",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lader med maksimal effekt med det samme, uanset solproduktion eller eltarif."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lädt sofort mit maximaler Leistung, unabhängig von Solarproduktion oder Stromtarif."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Charge immédiatement à puissance maximale, indépendamment de la production solaire ou du tarif électrique."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Carica immediatamente alla massima potenza, indipendentemente dalla produzione solare o dalla tariffa elettrica."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Charges your car only when enough solar power is available. Charging speed adjusts automatically based on current solar production.": {
      "comment": "Description of a charging mode when the user selects \"Charges your car only when enough solar power is available.\"",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Oplader kun din bil, når der er nok solenergi tilgængelig. Ladehastigheden tilpasses automatisk efter den aktuelle solproduktion."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lädt dein Auto nur, wenn genügend Solarstrom verfügbar ist. Die Ladegeschwindigkeit passt sich automatisch an die aktuelle Solarproduktion an."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Charge votre voiture uniquement lorsque suffisamment d'énergie solaire est disponible. La vitesse de charge s'adapte automatiquement à la production solaire actuelle."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Carica la tua auto solo quando è disponibile abbastanza energia solare. La velocità di carica si adatta automaticamente alla produzione solare attuale."
          }
        }
      }
    },
