    "Please note that the effect highly depends if the tvOS system setting is 'dark' or 'light' mode. Try change the system setting as well.": {
      "comment": "A footnote explaining the effect of changing the background image in relation to the device's system dark mode setting.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vær opmærksom på, at effekten i høj grad afhænger af, om tvOS-systemindstillingen er 'mørk' eller 'lys' tilstand. Prøv også at ændre systemindstillingen."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Bitte beachte, dass der Effekt stark vom Dunkel- oder Hell-Modus in den tvOS-Systemeinstellungen abhängt. Versuche, die Systemeinstellung ebenfalls zu ändern."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Please note that the effect highly depends if the tvOS system setting is 'dark' or 'light' mode. Try change the system setting as well."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Veuillez noter que l'effet dépend fortement du mode « sombre » ou « clair » des réglages système tvOS. Essayez également de modifier le réglage système."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si prega di notare che l'effetto dipende fortemente dalla modalità \"scura\" o \"chiara\" dell'impostazione di sistema tvOS. Prova a cambiare anche l'impostazione di sistema."
          }
        }
      }
    },
