    "You can ask Siri thinkg like the following:": {
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du kan spørge Siri om ting som følgende:"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sie können Siri Dinge wie die folgenden fragen:"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You can ask Siri thinkg like the following:"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vous pouvez demander à Siri des choses comme ceci:"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Puoi chiedere a Siri cose come le seguenti:"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can talk to Siri to get informaiton from you Solar Manager installtion or to control thinks like car charging mode.": {
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du kan tale med Siri for at få information fra din Solar Manager-installation eller for at styre ting som bilopladningstilstand."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sie können mit Siri sprechen, um Informationen von Ihrer Solar Manager-Installation zu erhalten oder Dinge wie den Autolademodus zu steuern."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You can talk to Siri to get informaiton from you Solar Manager installtion or to control thinks like car charging mode."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vous pouvez parler à Siri pour obtenir des informations de votre installation Solar Manager ou pour contrôler des éléments tels que le mode de charge de la voiture."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Puoi parlare con Siri per ottenere informazioni dalla tua installazione di Solar Manager o per controllare cose come la modalità di ricarica dell'auto."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can use Siri to query and control your Solar Manager using Solar Lens. This works everywhere where Siri works and therefore also in CarPlay etc. \n\nHere are some examples:": {
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du kan bruge Siri til at forespørge og styre din Solar Manager ved hjælp af Solar Lens. Dette virker overalt, hvor Siri virker og derfor også i CarPlay osv.\n\nHer er nogle eksempler:\t"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sie können mit Siri Ihren Solar Manager abfragen und kontrollieren. Dies funktioniert überall wo auch Siri zur verfügung steht wie z.B. in CarPlay.\n\nHier einige Beispiele:"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You can use Siri to query and control your Solar Manager using Solar Lens. This works everywhere where Siri works and therefore also in CarPlay etc. \n\nHere are some examples:"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ous pouvez utiliser Siri pour interroger et contrôler votre Solar Manager à l'aide de Solar Lens. Cela fonctionne partout où Siri fonctionne et donc aussi dans CarPlay, etc.\n\nVoici quelques exemples:"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Puoi usare Siri per interrogare e controllare il tuo Solar Manager usando Solar Lens. Questo funziona ovunque Siri funzioni e quindi anche in CarPlay ecc. \n\nEcco alcuni esempi:"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You find a lot more samples in the settings menu of Solar Lens.": {
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du finder mange flere eksempler i indstillingsmenuen i Solar Lens."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sie finden viele weitere Beispiele im Einstellungsmenü von Solar Lens."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You find a lot more samples in the settings menu of Solar Lens."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vous trouverez beaucoup plus d'exemples dans le menu des réglages de Solar Lens."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Troverai molti altri esempi nel menu delle impostazioni di Solar Lens."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You need to add the words 'in Solar Lens' to your Siri commands.": {
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du skal tilføje ordene 'i Solar Lens' til dine Siri-kommandoer."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sie müssen die Worte 'in Solar Lens' zu Ihren Siri-Befehlen hinzufügen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You need to add the words 'in Solar Lens' to your Siri commands."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vous devez ajouter les mots « dans Solar Lens » à vos commandes Siri."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Devi aggiungere le parole 'in Solar Lens' ai tuoi comandi Siri."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You will find more information in Solar Lens settgins menu.": {
      "localizations": {
        "da": {
          "stringUnit": {
